<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mobile App Screen</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>My App</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="primary">
            <h2>Primary Section</h2>
            <p>This section uses the primary color (#4CAF50).</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="secondary">
            <h2>Secondary Section</h2>
            <p>This section uses the secondary color (#FFC107).</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="accent">
            <h2>Accent Section</h2>
            <p>This section uses the accent color (#2196F3).</p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>


Updated Example with Applied Colors:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mobile App Screen</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>My App</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="primary">
            <h2>Primary Section</h2>
            <p>This section uses the primary color (#4CAF50).</p>
            <button class="primary-btn">Primary Button</button>
        </section>
        
        <section class="secondary">
            <h2>Secondary Section</h2>
            <p>This section uses the secondary color (#FFC107).</p>
            <button class="secondary-btn">Secondary Button</button>
        </section>
        
        <section class="accent">
            <h2>Accent Section</h2>
            <p>This section uses the accent color (#2196F3).</p>
            <button class="accent-btn">Accent Button</button>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
